reviewText: I enjoyed all of these movies but Betty Lou is just what most women feel like at times.  Glossed over and subhuman.  She did the part very well but the best scene is in the bathroom.  What a hoot!  Gross Anatomy and Betsy's Wedding are fun films too but Betty Lou does rock.

reviewText: I bought this for two of the movies, the "Gun in Betty Lou's Handbag" and "Betsy's Wedding."  I'm not going to review the movies, I bought this because I love them. The DVD was in excellent condition, I watched each movie separately with no problems. There are no real extras, there seldom are with these multi-movie sets.  But for the price I wouldn't expect any.  I don't think there are any edits from the originals, if there are I didn't catch them so they wouldn't be significant.  All in all it was a good deal.
